<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span>الْأَمر فِيهَا<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p58"></span>أَو يصطلحا<a href="#p58" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p59"></span>على شئ<a href="#p59" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
