<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>الْعين<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>فِي يدهما وَأَقَامَا بينتين بقيت<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p63"></span>فِي يدهما<a href="#p63" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p64"></span>كَمَا كَانَت<a href="#p64" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p65"></span>أَولا على قَول التساقط وَتجْعَل بَينهمَا على قَول الْقِسْمَة<a href="#p65" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
